{"tid":1434359,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 建議將「不推文回覆」改為預設選項","createTime":"2019-08-08T18:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T20:40:51.000Z","uid":163024,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3b64bf08d3dd348a2c95c7dd198fac58181e89d4","tid":1434359,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:04:11.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n除咗要處理「有部份post下面即使有大量『不推文回覆』仍然上到熱門」呢個漏洞對外，我覺得呢點都好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">有關該漏洞嘅post: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430903</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日我見到幾個post叫大家「善用不推文回覆功能」但係都上唔到熱門<br />\n我明白要大家平時覆post撳多一個option係麻煩啲，我自己都成日會因為懶/唔記得咗而無用到呢個功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其要大家做多一步，不如直接將「不推文回覆」呢個選項改為預設?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣做除咗可以有效打擊三毛、令真正有用嘅post上熱門之外，仲可以避免一啲無咁相關但多人討論嘅post誤上熱門</span><br />\n<br />\n缺點除咗會令到個熱門比較單調之外，就係要大家平時推post果陣要撳多個option，不過我個人就覺得如果一個post嘅價值係大到你肯主動幫佢推post嘅話，你都唔會在意呢啲小事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家同唔同意? 有咩睇法?"},{"pid":"02f24c54605bea0b39814d9e5adaf20c02003004","tid":1434359,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:04:57.000Z","msg":"自推10次，跟住就訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b62a14fefce63aea526d25cb27a84db04eb725b","tid":1434359,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:08.000Z","msg":"0"},{"pid":"db9babad18b7e479e718e02ab4cbd9e602a25a40","tid":1434359,"uid":179402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「幫幫手推一推」黑警唔單止搜身時恐嚇市民 仲要強光照市民對眼！ | LIHKG</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434132/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF74MRhonX28&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCN2UZYMvR53lMa2%2BnKJB5b4%3D&h=1e8048f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F74MRhonX28</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOjM9aG3xZKk&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCN2UZYMvR53lMa2%2BnKJB5b4%3D&h=126996ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OjM9aG3xZKk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有乜野必要同理由對市民使用強光照住佢對眼？呢個行為有咩意義同對工作上有咩幫助？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">強烈要求黑警回應點解要用惡劣 粗暴 令人不適嘅態度 語氣 行為 去對待配合黑警工作嘅市民！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n幫手派出去 推上報<br />\n<br />\n今次拍片者冇事 下個好難講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fa829dd29c3a7219043c6afc139e1881d89a67","tid":1434359,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"127533c35555c0d6f1800a41d508b367e0367d05","tid":1434359,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:39.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e81c9cfbc6e3d3671f39439ab3f48096bf690d84","tid":1434359,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a0e8a61bc68c163aa38e8d5211b581b7babe967d","tid":1434359,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:06:08.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c151d2ce16ead312525d4a30caa523f7448a034c","tid":1434359,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f5f9a5039150ccd0cc9c0a8